298
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:54,240
And you've been somewhat subdued

299
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:56,270
since we left Zevil Island.

300
00:19:57,840 --> 00:20:00,940
My target was Hisoka.

301
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:05,680
I waited for the perfect chance
