314
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:12,040
After that, I was pretty
miserable and lonely.

315
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:16,040
I felt so helpless,

316
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:18,760
I wanted company...

317
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:21,170
I wanted to help someone,

318
00:21:21,820 --> 00:21:23,060
I guess.

319
00:21:24,050 --> 00:21:26,850
That's why I was looking for you two.

320
00:21:27,420 --> 00:21:28,210
Gon.

321
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,380
Leorio and I have only been able

322
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:34,250
to make it this far because of you.

323
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:38,650
We're truly grateful.

324
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:44,610
I'd also like to thank you.

325
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:52,130
Gon has deepened his bond
with his friends.

